{"tid":324265,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[入黎三文魚幫你含] 脆皮香煎三文魚配白汁蘑菇","createTime":"2017-07-16T09:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T13:05:16.000Z","uid":38923,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47e699be90b9a536816451f201ac707a9a680868","tid":324265,"uid":38923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:59:24.000Z","msg":"今日終於得閑出食譜，圖有啲矇，有錯勿屌<br />\n<br />\n材料普通超市都有，不過香草要去Taste買<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">材料:</span></span><br />\n三文魚<br />\n蘑菇<br />\nCream<br />\n蒜茸<br />\nSalt &amp; pepper<br />\n茜/Parsley<br />\nThyme (有就加 冇就算)<br />\n白酒 (有就加 冇就算)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/LNfC21gl.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLNfC21gl.gif&h=259f0a4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先三文魚刨鱗，小心慢慢刨，唔好太大力整甩塊皮<br />\n唔知點解超市唔刨佐鱗先切件，好似留啲鱗新鮮啲咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/g5JWVsTl.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fg5JWVsTl.gif&h=9dddf03b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沖一沖塊魚 然後用kitchen towel印乾<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/pK0eaZxl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpK0eaZxl.jpg&h=a4fdb2e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乾佐之後加鹽<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/1T3HBZBl.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1T3HBZBl.gif&h=113c0eed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為唔係好大塊 所以唔洗界坑<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">開pan</span></span><br />\n我鍾意不銹鋼pan 因為可以加到好熱又唔會有化學物質<br />\n但不銹鋼PAN要時間開pan  同埋會好大油煙<br />\n<br />\n唔好落油  用大火燒熱個pan 大概半分鐘至1分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/STDily4l.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSTDily4l.gif&h=4caeb189&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要試佢夠唔夠熱可以加啲水  如果一粒粒水珠轉下轉下就代表夠熱<br />\n<br />\n落油  一定用植物油 欖油太熱會變<br />\n落多少少要搽得哂成個pan<br />\n<br />\n等油開始出煙同聞到油煙味果時可以熄火<br />\n等個pan凍 可以倒走多餘既油<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qiSoDuJl.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqiSoDuJl.gif&h=488a9950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個時候個pan上面有層防黏塗層 可以見到反光  <br />\n可以開始煎<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/NaGOq3Al.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNaGOq3Al.gif&h=c7bffcfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落魚 先煎皮<br />\n用中細火慢煎  如果好似Gordon咁大火煎塊皮燶佐入面都未煎得熟<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/dcM4Od2l.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdcM4Od2l.gif&h=4e663a38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n慢慢等佢煎  三文魚有個好處係熟佐會變色，所以好易睇得出煎成點<br />\n<br />\n當白色上到一半至2/3就可以準備反<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/gP5njvvl.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgP5njvvl.gif&h=e9f90ce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反一定用鑊鏟  唔好用鉗夾  因為會散<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/eT2djb0l.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeT2djb0l.gif&h=4c5a874d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n慢慢煎到兩邊白色遇上  再煎多半分鐘(怕生)之後可以熄火<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/6kV3w6Vl.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6kV3w6Vl.gif&h=52b1addf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蘑菇汁:<br />\n</span></span>蘑菇薄切 (唔洗驚太大塊 因為熟佐size縮一半)<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/iDMhXo3l.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FiDMhXo3l.gif&h=4be6b35d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用返頭先個pan中大火炒<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/xUaXAKGl.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxUaXAKGl.gif&h=4e6d25d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7 8成熟加蒜茸同香草(thyme如果有) 轉中細火<br />\n太早加蒜茸會好易燶  所以後加<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/OLcUqIXl.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOLcUqIXl.gif&h=703aea14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加白酒 (如果有 但我冇)<br />\n加Cream<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/8Nc8i6Il.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8Nc8i6Il.gif&h=12383b40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大火收汁<br />\n<br />\n想杰啲可以加多啲cream或少少麵粉<br />\n<br />\n最後切啲茜加落去<br />\n上碟<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/7toAuGIl.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7toAuGIl.gif&h=a16fdcc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同場加映</span></span><br />\n<strong>松露蘑菇忌廉意粉</strong><br />\n<br />\n用剩蘑菇汁唔好晒<br />\n<br />\n材料<br />\n<br />\n意粉<br />\n蘑菇汁<br />\n蒜頭<br />\n芝士(車打/Parmesan)<br />\n松露醬<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/veoUlqNl.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FveoUlqNl.gif&h=f2fb1232&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加鹽落熱水  煮意粉<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Q5pXKoRl.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQ5pXKoRl.gif&h=17d80040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蒜頭切粒<br />\n<br />\n細火慢煎蒜頭粒<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/pdiMz0Cl.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpdiMz0Cl.gif&h=218be628&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開始有少少金黃加蘑菇汁<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0AwNzD1l.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0AwNzD1l.gif&h=ba3f3dcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加意粉  之後加芝士<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/DIbLH6zl.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDIbLH6zl.gif&h=9e282dc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後加松露醬<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/wF4eM1Nl.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwF4eM1Nl.gif&h=d9c77db8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上碗<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/uk9AX2vl.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fuk9AX2vl.gif&h=f6bbf513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(矇)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nReference:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.greatbritishchefs.com/recipes/pan-fried-salmon-recipe-mushroom-sauce\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.greatbritishchefs.com%2Frecipes%2Fpan-fried-salmon-recipe-mushroom-sauce&d=rxk17erlJZ36AQF4Z7uN2xxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=2bb7939b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.greatbritishchefs.com/recipes/pan-fried-salmon-recipe-mushroom-sauce</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jD9VJ92xyzA?t=2m27s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjD9VJ92xyzA%3Ft%3D2m27s&d=rxk17erlJZ36AQF4Z7uN2xxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=092deffe\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jD9VJ92xyzA?t=2m27s</a><br />\n<br />\n&emsp;"},{"pid":"228872f2cbde4c1ca29e65be661dc162c1c42175","tid":324265,"uid":68352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:02:25.000Z","msg":"好似死圖"},{"pid":"fc3ffe09bee4fed00c4d5221db21746afabf7480","tid":324265,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:03:46.000Z","msg":"想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d4bfb83e984ddb5e2e71136ebb319a44adbcd2","tid":324265,"uid":38923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:08:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似死圖</blockquote><br />\n屌呀"},{"pid":"ecc544f627055f9bad0b752d2ebecc28e839f6f0","tid":324265,"uid":38923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:09:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似死圖</blockquote><br />\n屌呀</blockquote><br />\n電腦睇冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8a5415ee48e98fb6e0d0fcebb8e20e51035909","tid":324265,"uid":1672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:11:01.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548a92e3ad16b16438e27900df98e7cf5343d4bb","tid":324265,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:15:19.000Z","msg":"巴打,加d porcini重菇味d<br />\n煎得好靚,不過唔好三文<em><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </em>"},{"pid":"3960702edd7aa5467f47b6d91f746835d31b7718","tid":324265,"uid":38923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:37:26.000Z","msg":"點解電話睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7d098a0ee2c0c24061fed931d276ba7a3044a0","tid":324265,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T10:39:26.000Z","msg":"見到個POST名估到係早兩日個個"},{"pid":"d60654bcad2aee3eb5b0b71af6f002d8dc364f7d","tid":324265,"uid":38923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T12:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b497593083b93f0fd37223951aeedea012d2c5d8","tid":324265,"uid":68661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T13:05:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解電話睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\niphone用app睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}